	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />- I really enjoyed Super CastleVania IV, mainly because it's a 16-bit highly improved version of its 8-bit counterpart. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" /> Who cares if the gfx looks blocky or whatever? It has some awesome backgrounds, a great music and so on! Cool! 
<br />
<br />- Dracula X (SNES version) is a bad remake of the original Rondo of the Blood. They're, in fact, different games. Yup, it brings a few better things, but CV4 is better. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />

		

		</td>
	</tr>
