		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Though I like Dracula X, I have to agree that it is completely different from Rondo of Blood. I don't know why they didn't make a decent port of that game to the SNES; it's completely doable. And plus, you can't play as Maria, who totally owns over Richter.

		

